{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Description\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab deletes leftover short notes, that are created, when splitting (on grid) notes that are not hard quantized (humanized)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab this script works in arrangement, MIDI Editor and Inline Editor\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab adjust the length of shortnote in the user area. To get an idea which values are typical for short notes, enable the ShowConsoleMsg near the end of the script\sa180\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
