{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Description\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab this script human quantizes either all notes or selected notes by 50% to the 1/1 grid\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab this script works in arrangement, MIDI Editor and Inline Editor\sa180\par}
}

