{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Description\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab this script moves the edit cursor by frames depending on the value sent by the mousewheel.\sa180\par}
}

