{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Description\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab this script either stops the playback (when transport is playing) or returns to the last cursor positions (when transport is stopped) and mimics the Cubase behavior of the 0 NumPad key\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab no undo will be created for this script\sa180\par}
}

